    <item>
      <title>咖啡豆价格上涨叠加能源成本攀升，独立咖啡馆经营正进入“薄利高压期”</title>
      <link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/ka-pei-dou-jie-ge-shang-zhang-die-jia-neng-yuan-ch/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 18:37:26 +0800</pubDate>
